  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors nominally addressed; however, two factors (Numerical solver error and Relevance of the validation activities to the COU) are carried as not-assessed on grounds that they were considered beyond the scope of the current submission cycle.",
